definitions.definition: Any of several species of horse-like animals, especially Equus asinus , the domesticated of which are used as beasts of burden .
( often vulgar through confusion with other word ) A stupid or jerky (inconsiderate, etc) person.
examples: That new kid left the cap off the syrup bottle again! What an ass .

main_definition: Any of several species of horse-like animals, especially Equus asinus , the domesticated of which are used as beasts of burden .
secondary_definitions: ( often vulgar through confusion with other word ) A stupid or jerky (inconsiderate, etc) person.

definitions.definition: Sex ; a person to have sex with; with vulgar emphasis on their corporeality (their body ) over their personhood .
examples: I'm going to go down to the bar and try to get me some ass .

definitions.definition: Used in similes to express something bad or unpleasant .
A person ; the self ; ( reflexively ) oneself or one's person , chiefly their body . By extension, one's personal safety, or figuratively one's job, prospects, etc.
examples: Get your lazy ass out of bed!
We risk our asses out there every day.
I'ma get medieval on your ass !
Mess up one more time and it's your ass (i.e. you're fired)

secondary_definitions: ( synecdochically , uncountable ) Sex ; a person to have sex with; with vulgar emphasis on their corporeality (their body ) over their personhood .
( uncountable ) Used in similes to express something bad or unpleasant .
( synecdochically , countable ) A person ; the self ; ( reflexively ) oneself or one's person , chiefly their body . By extension, one's personal safety, or figuratively one's job, prospects, etc.
